sp;.dw Reset<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;.dw IRQ<br /><br />;----------------------------------------------------------------<br />; CHR-ROM bank<br />;----------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp;.incbin &quot;Graphics.chr&quot;</div></div>

